Description: Hexagon Composites ASA is a Norway-based composite cylinder technology company. The Company enables the safe delivery of clean energy in gaseous form to homes and industries and decarbonizes transportation on land and at sea. Hexagon is organized into four business areas: Hexagon Agility, Hexagon Ragasco, Hexagon Digital Wave and Hexagon Purus. Hexagon Agility is a global provider of clean fuel solutions for commercial vehicles and gas transportation solutions. Hexagon Ragasco is the manufacturer of composite liquefied petroleum gas (LPG) cylinders for leisure, household and industrial applications. Hexagon Digital Wave is engaged in cylinder testing and monitoring technologies, offering solutions that reduce down-time and inspection costs while improving inspection accuracy. Hexagon Purus is offers solutions within key technologies needed for zero emission mobility.

Author: Malin Noem
